```

## 🔧 请求封装使用规范

### 1. Alova 请求使用
```typescript
// API 定义
import { alovaInstance } from '@/http/alova'

export const getUserInfo = () => {
  return alovaInstance.Get('/user/info')
}

// 组件中使用
import { useRequest } from 'alova/client'
import { getUserInfo } from '@/api/user'

const { loading, data, error, send } = useRequest(getUserInfo, {
  immediate: true
})
```

### 2. 错误处理
```typescript
const { loading, data, error, send } = useRequest(apiMethod, {
  immediate: true,
  onError: (error) => {
    toast.error(error.message || '请求失败')
  }
})
```

